on due to vorticity. Such a fast\namplification will have implications for a wide array of topics related to\nsmall-scale fields in the lower atmosphere, particularly with regard to\npropagating wave phenomena in MBPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Nov 2019 18:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-15"}
