namics are\nconsistent with time series data that has been collected at a banded vegetation\nsite. This fast-slow model framework introduces a tool for investigating the\npossible impact of changes to frequency and intensity of rain events in dryland\necosystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Nov 2019 18:26:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 May 2020 14:40:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-24"}
