 Hamiltonian\nwhich can explain the electronic structure of each polymorph of halide\nperovskites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2019 10:34:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 15 Apr 2020 09:22:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-17"}
